{"tid":1692331,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【做乜啫？】陳偉霆騎呢MV翻唱大陸神曲 洪欣被讚人靚聲甜","createTime":"2019-11-04T04:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T09:57:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8012ccfae644a7be202bcb05a1243cdfff450580","tid":1692331,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:34:06.000Z","msg":"大陸歌手董寶石推出的歌曲《野狼DISCO》，其騎呢廣東話發音及洗腦式曲風，最近熱爆，就連洪欣同陳偉霆亦忍不住拍MV翻唱，雖然好有誠意，但陳偉霆（William）個MV就貫徹歌曲風格，一樣騎呢。<br />\n這首在17年推出的《野狼DISCO》，因為早前因原唱在大陸節目《中國新說唱》中表演而震驚14億人，被網民喻為神曲的《野》，MV的播放量更高達10億次。一向走在尖端的William，早前就拍MV翻唱該曲。只見在MV中，身穿黑Tee襯波褲，造型配搭極騎呢的William，背向鏡頭抓着路邊的路牌，深情地唱該曲的廣東話部份，之後William又找了日落黃昏做背景，然後側坐在大石上，擺出以雙手支撐着向後傾的銷魂pose繼續唱，唱到最後更索性舉高一隻腳，畫面毫無美感不特止，更可以用騎呢來形容。雖然騎呢，但fans看完亦紛紛留言表示喜歡，甚至更有人搞笑地說：「屁股好翹，幼腿好細，眼神好勾人。」<br />\n至於同樣有拍MV翻唱《野》曲的洪欣，比起William就正常得多，在MV開始，她先以太陽眼鏡配黑西裝上陣，之後又換上藍白間條恤衫、藍色大褸配牛仔褲拍攝，雖然該MV只得30秒，但洪欣就唱得非常認真，與William的騎呢MV有極大對比。難得洪欣開口唱歌，網民亦一致認為洪欣「人美聲甜」，o氹得洪欣非常開心，留言表示要多謝大家的讚賞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191103/large/1572790737_aeda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191103%2Flarge%2F1572790737_aeda.jpg&h=1c7d8a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191103/60227679\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191103%2F60227679&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfmsgcJLaMXzh2FZp7TjlN88%3D&h=4a5c5a68\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191103%2F60227679&h=13d3e696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191103/60227679</a>"},{"pid":"b14a9029c99102a25793e27fdc07a64898ff96c5","tid":1692331,"uid":45749,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:43:07.000Z","msg":"快撚啲捧紅佢"},{"pid":"dda2b579228d738b174027b7032d8aa3a099c05f","tid":1692331,"uid":78755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:45:43.000Z","msg":"唔係想捧佢拍mv黎把撚呀<br />\n<br />\n快撚啲捧紅佢tim呀"},{"pid":"4d430e981b8905aac80710529b3fcaaf2ea84594","tid":1692331,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dda2b579228d738b174027b7032d8aa3a099c05f","tid":1692331,"uid":78755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:45:43.000Z","msg":"唔係想捧佢拍mv黎把撚呀<br />\n<br />\n快撚啲捧紅佢tim呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:35:58.000Z","msg":"有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65d1dbb3747a518bd9f5167b0f06d23cb4a401c","tid":1692331,"uid":117412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:36:52.000Z","msg":"@宇宙第一美人<br />\n上水喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a533e9c6c84eeaadb76ca6f480d73614a61b384b","tid":1692331,"uid":49859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:43:21.000Z","msg":"見到洪欣就知個post會好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752d489106303594aa9d5f63d6ea4e63196954d9","tid":1692331,"uid":68661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236d6e682b448c98fc13172544c3d3ebdb499c7f","tid":1692331,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"752d489106303594aa9d5f63d6ea4e63196954d9","tid":1692331,"uid":68661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T07:31:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c8345c072df923f44422aa66e7971a5e37c33d","tid":1692331,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q